# NSG Rules YAML - {{REPO_INFRA_NAME}}

## Format

List of rules with required fields:

```yaml
- name: "RuleName"
  priority: 100
  direction: "Inbound" | "Outbound"
  access: "Allow" | "Deny"
  protocol: "*" | "Tcp" | "Udp"
  source_port_range: "*"
  destination_port_range: "*" | "443" | ...
  source_address_prefix: "VirtualNetwork" | "*" | "10.0.0.0/8" | ...
  destination_address_prefix: "VirtualNetwork" | "*" | ...
```

## Optional fields

- `source_address_prefixes`: list (replaces source_address_prefix)
- `destination_port_ranges`: list (replaces destination_port_range)

## Conventions

- Final Deny priority: 4096
- Naming: PascalCase or PascalCase + descriptive (e.g. AllowInboundVnetToVnet)
